Those called caraya are the most numerous and the ugliest species, Their hair is tawny, they are full of melancholy‚ always querulous, always morose, always snap÷ pish. As they howl incessantly day and night no one chooses to take them home and tame them. They sit by crowds on πεῖθε, and wander about in search of food.
